1. *Uzme* ličnu kartu iz džepa i pažljivo je pregleda. (He took his ID card out of the pocket and looked at it carefully.)

2. *Uze* je vazduh duboko u pluća. (She took a deep breath.)

3. *Uzima* se neko vreme da se savlada novi jezik. (It takes some time to master a new language.)

4. *Uzeli* su ga za ruku i zajedno su otišli. (They took him by the hand and went away together.)

5. *Uzeće* ona nešto da se odmori. (She will take something to rest.)